Text: Hey Steve, how big of a place are you looking for ? I have a 1/1 condo available for $1,750 a month. Close to downtown St. Pete
Hi Martin, we will be out by 10am today. One more trip left to go
Ok, thank you Steve, all good with the move ?

Yes thank you. And everything was great at your Airbnb. 

Id still like to grab that coffee and Melissa will join if she can. We moved to 

2649 Tifton St. S
Gulfport, FL 33711

So we aren’t far away. And we can’t extend beyond the 1-year lease we signed so I’m already thinking of where we will be next and would like to learn more about the area. Ay, I apologize missed the last text from you! Absolutely, how is tomorrow for afternoon ? Or during lunch ?
Tomorrow I am out of town. How about Friday afternoon? Or Thursday around lunch time

Martin, I didn’t hear back so I didn’t reserve my calendar for the afternoon. Apologies on that. I will be downtown Gulfport tomorrow for the parade and volleyball open if you’re around then
No just watching they are all very good
